-charts.com |publisher=Hung Medien |accessdate=August 23, 2013}}</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:2.5em;font-size:90%;\"| [[Official New Zealand Music Chart|NZ]]<br /><ref name=\"NZ\">{{cite web |url=https://charts.nz/showinterpret.asp?interpret=Imagine+Dragons |title=Discography Imagine Dragons |work=charts.nz |publisher=Hung Medien |accessdate=March 28, 2013}}</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:2.5em;font-size:90%;\"| [[Swiss Hitparade|SWI]]<br /><ref name=\"SWI\">{{cite web |url=http://swisscharts.com/showinterpret.asp?interpret=Imagine+Dragons |title=Discography Imagine Dragons |work=swisscharts.com |publisher=Hung Medien |accessdate=November 7, 2012}}</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:2.5em;font-size:90%;\"| [[UK Albums Chart|UK]]<br /><ref name=\"UK-albums\">{{cite web |url=https://www.officialcharts.com/artist/26279/imagine-dragons/ |title=Imagine Dragons |publisher=[[Official Charts Company]] |accessdate=November 17, 2018 |format=select \"Albums\" tab }}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| ''[[Night Visions]]''\n|\n* Released: September 4, 2012 {{small|(US)}}<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.allmusic.com/album/night-visions-mw0002409529 |title=The Vision \u2013 Imagine Dragons |work=[[AllMusic]] |publisher=[[Rovi Corporation]] |accessdate=September 21, 2012 |author=Heaney, Gregory}}</ref>\n* Label: [[Interscope Records|Interscope]], [[Kidinakorner]]\n* Formats: [[Compact disc|CD]], [[Music download|DL]], [[Gramophone record|LP]]\n| 2 || 1 || 4 || 3 || 15 || 6 || 3 || 5 || 9 || 2\n|\n* WW: 7,000,000<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.lastampa.it/2015/02/10/spettacoli/festival-di-sanremo/2015/sanremo-imagine-dragons-per-noi-litalia-sinonimo-di-musica-lirica-NTo2dgReFgx9TWj1xCEDiM/pagina.html|title=Imagine Dragons: \"Per noi l\u2019Italia \u00e8 sinonimo di musica lirica\"|date=10 February 2015|work=LaStampa.it}}</ref>\n* [[Nielsen SoundScan|US]]: 2,400,000<ref>{{cite web|url=http://hitsdailydouble.com/news&id=294697|title=Dragons Get Targeted|last=|first=|date=Febru