IB92 |title=Imagine Dragons \u2013 Ep: Imagine Dragons |work=[[Amazon.com]] |accessdate=September 21, 2012}}</ref>\n* Formats: CD, DL\n|\u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 \n|\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| ''[[Hell and Silence]]''\n|\n* Released: June 1, 2010 {{small|(US)}}<ref name=\"Hell and Silence: Imagine Dragons\">{{cite web |url=https://www.amazon.com/Hell-and-Silence/dp/B003PY3J1U |title=Hell and Silence: Imagine Dragons |work=[[Amazon.com]] |accessdate=September 21, 2012}}</ref>\n* Formats: CD, DL\n| \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014\n|\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| ''[[It's Time (EP)|It's Time]]''\n|\n* Released: March 12, 2011 {{small|(US)}}<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.amazon.com/Its-Time/dp/B004RT5SMU |title=It's Time: Imagine Dragons |work=[[Amazon.com]] |accessdate=September 21, 2012}}</ref>\n* Formats: CD, DL\n| \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014\n|\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| ''[[Continued Silence EP]]''\n|\n* Released: February 14, 2012 {{small|(US)}}<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.allmusic.com/album/continued-silence-ep-mw0002315310 |title=Continued Silence EP \u2013 Imagine Dragons |publisher=[[Rovi Corporation]] |work=[[AllMusic]] |accessdate=September 21, 2012 |author=Lymangrover, Jason}}</ref>\n* Label: Interscope\n* Formats: CD, DL\n| 40 || 8 || 11 || 86 || 20\n|\n* BPI: Gold<ref name=\"BPI\"/>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| ''[[Hear Me (EP)|Hear Me]]''\n|\n* Released: November 25, 2012 {{small|(UK)}}<ref>{{cite web |url=https://itunes.apple.com/gb/album/hear-me-ep/id570919085 |title=Hear Me \u2013 EP by Imagine Dragons |work=[[iTunes Store]] |publisher=[[Apple Inc.|Apple]] |accessdate=January 21, 2013}}</ref>\n* Label: Interscope\n* Formats: CD, DL\n| \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014\n|\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| ''[[The Archive (EP)|The Archive]]''\n|\n* Released: February 12, 2013 {{small|(US)}}<ref>{{cite web |url=https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/the-archive-ep/id598698945 |title=The Archive \u2013 EP by Imagine Dragons 