 of Extinction]]''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[Warriors (Imagine Dragons song)|Warriors]]\"\n| \u2014{{efn|group=upper-alpha|\"Warriors\" did not enter the ''Billboard'' Hot 100, but peaked at number two on the [[Bubbling Under Hot 100 Singles]] chart, which acts as a quasi-extension to the Hot 100.<ref name=\"US-Bubbling-singles\">{{cite web |url=http://www.billboard.com/music/imagine-dragons/chart-history/bubbling-under-hot-100 |title=Imagine Dragons \u2013 Chart History: Bubbling Under Hot 100 |work=Billboard |accessdate=July 24, 2018}}</ref>}} || 10 || \u2014 || 60 || 48 || 58 || 80 || \u2014 || \u2014 || 54\n|\n* US: 478,241<ref>{{cite web |title=Billboard Digital Songs Chart Week Ending May 25, 2017 |url=http://www.defjampromo.com/files/2009/10/BB-Digital-Songs-Chart-Wk.-Ending-5-25-17.pdf |publisher=[[Nielsen SoundScan]] |accessdate=April 12, 2019 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190412162037/http://www.defjampromo.com/files/2009/10/BB-Digital-Songs-Chart-Wk.-Ending-5-25-17.pdf |archivedate=April 12, 2019 |date=May 30, 2017}}</ref>\n|\n* RIAA: Platinum<ref name=\"RIAA\"/>\n* BPI: Silver<ref name=\"BPI\"/>\n| ''[[The Divergent Series: Insurgent \u2013 Original Motion Picture Soundtrack|The Divergent Series: Insurgent]]''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[I Bet My Life]]\"\n| 28 || 3 || 36 || 15 || 42 || 65 || 40 || 28 || 71 || 27\n|\n|\n* RIAA: Platinum<ref name=\"RIAA\"/>\n* BPI: Silver<ref name=\"BPI\"/>\n* MC: 3\u00d7 Platinum<ref name=\"MC\"/>\n|rowspan=\"3\"| ''Smoke + Mirrors''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[Gold (Imagine Dragons song)|Gold]]\"\n| \u2014 || 12 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014\n|\n|\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[Shots (Imagine Dragons song)|Shots]]\"\n| rowspan=\"3\"| 2015\n| 75 || 7 || 66 || 72 || 170 || 60 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || 91\n| \n|\n* BPI: Silver<ref name=\"BPI\"/>\n* BVMI: Gold<ref name=\"BVMI\"/>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[Roots (song)|Roots]]\"\n| 77 || 5 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2