games-catching-fire-original-motion-picture-soundtrack-mw0002585397 |title=The Hunger Games: Catching Fire [Original Motion Picture Soundtrack] \u2013 Various Artists |work=[[AllMusic]] |publisher=[[Rovi Corporation]] |accessdate=November 30, 2013 |author=Phares, Heather}}</ref>\n| [[The Hunger Games: Catching Fire \u2013 Original Motion Picture Soundtrack|''The Hunger Games: Catching Fire'']]\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"30 Lives\" (original demo)<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/life/music/2013/11/25/songs-for-the-philippines-album-compilation/3704555 |title=New album uses hit songs to aid Philippines |work=[[USA Today]] |publisher=[[Gannett Company]] |date=November 25, 2013 |accessdate=June 11, 2014 |author=Desta, Yohana}}</ref>\n| ''Songs for the Philippines''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Heart Upon My Sleeve\"<br><span style=\"font-size:85%;\">(with [[Avicii]])</span>\n| 2019\n| ''[[Tim (Avicii album)|Tim]]''\n|}\n\n==Music videos==\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|+ List of music videos, showing year released and director\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:18em;\"| Title\n! scope=\"col\"| Year\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:16em;\"| Director(s)\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Uptight\"\n| 2009\n| Luke Andrews<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rPUiAAHfsTs|title=Imagine Dragons - Uptight (Music Video)|first=|last=Imagine Dragons Daily|date=3 November 2015|publisher=|via=YouTube}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"It's Time\"\n| rowspan=\"2\"| 2012\n| Anthony Leonardi<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.mtv.com/videos/imagine-dragons/759371/its-time.jhtml |title=It's Time {{!}} Imagine Dragons {{!}} Music Video |work=[[MTV]] |publisher=[[Viacom Media Networks]] |date=April 17, 2012 |accessdate=December 15, 2013}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Radioactive\"\n| Syndrome<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.mtv.com/videos/imagine-dragons/864082/radioactive.jhtml |title=Radioactive {{!}} Imagine Dragons {{!}} Music Video |work=[[M