manager and coached the [[Algeria national football team]].\n\n==Club career==\n\n===Saint-\u00c9tienne===\n\n===Servette===\n\n===Bastia===\n\n===Clubs goals===\n====[[UEFA]] competitions====\n{| class=\"wikitable collapsible\"\n|-\n! # !! Date !! Venue !! Opponent !! Score !! Result !! Competition\n|-\n| 1. || 4 September 1957 || [[Ibrox Stadium]], [[Glasgow]], [[Scotland]] || {{flagicon|SCO}} [[Rangers F.C.|Rangers]] || style=\"text-align:center;\"| 0\u2013'''1'''<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.uefa.com/uefachampionsleague/season=1957/matches/round=900/match=61227/postmatch/lineups/index.html|title=Rangers 3\u20131 Saint-\u00c9tienne|publisher=UEFA.com|date=4 September 1957|accessdate=27 August 2015}}</ref> || style=\"text-align:center;\"| 3\u20131 || [[1957\u201358 European Cup]]\n|-\n| 2. || 12 September 1962 || [[Stade des Charmilles]], [[Gen\u00e8ve]], [[Switzerland]] || {{flagicon|NED}} [[Feyenoord]] || style=\"text-align:center;\"| '''1'''\u20130<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.uefa.com/uefachampionsleague/season=1962/matches/round=925/match=61881/postmatch/lineups/index.html|title=Servette 1\u20133 Feyenoord|publisher=UEFA.com|date=12 September 1962|accessdate=27 August 2015}}</ref> || style=\"text-align:center;\"| 1\u20133 || [[1962\u201363 European Cup]]\n|-\n| 3. || 19 September 1962 || [[De Kuip]], [[Rotterdam]], [[Netherlands]] || {{flagicon|NED}} [[Feyenoord]] || style=\"text-align:center;\"| 0\u2013'''1'''<ref name=\"Feyenoord\">{{cite web|url=http://www.uefa.com/uefachampionsleague/season=1962/matches/round=925/match=61882/postmatch/lineups/index.html|title=Feyenoord 1\u20133 Servette|publisher=UEFA.com|date=19 September 1962|accessdate=27 August 2015}}</ref> || style=\"text-align:center;\"| 1\u20133 || 1962\u201363 European Cup\n|-\n| 4. || 19 September 1962 || De Kuip, Rotterdam, Netherlands || {{flagicon|NED}} [[Feyenoord]] || style=\"text-align:center;\"| 0\u2013'''3'''<ref name=\"Feyenoord\"/> || style=\"text-align:center;\"| 1\u20133 || 1962\u20